{"tid":1185190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9．22罷課中大百萬大道集會","createTime":"2019-06-04T06:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T06:35:08.000Z","uid":50457,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6b86aa8f9a9d79ca864bf79d74b6b1d22825ce","tid":1185190,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"學聯秘書長周永康說，共有十多間院校的學生參與罷課，在首天於中大百萬大道集會後，他們會由院校走出社區，連結社會，在公民廣場、添馬公園等地方集會，暫難估計參與罷課學生人數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學聯稱，若罷課後人大仍不徹回決議，政府又不允諾在第二輪政改諮詢確認公民提名、修改基本法，他們的行動將會升級。<br />\n<br />\n另外，學民思潮也舉行中學生罷課商討會，約百名中學生出席。有表明參與罷課的中學生稱，會嘗試在政治活動與學習之間取得平衡，又認為家長不應因為不了解而反對罷課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20140907/s00001/1410083264596/9-22%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%93%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20140907%2Fs00001%2F1410083264596%2F9-22%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=7f84880c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20140907%2Fs00001%2F1410083264596%2F9-22%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583&h=3f7550d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20140907/s00001/1410083264596/9-22%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%93%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n呢次比8.31更關乎香港人的命運，大學生覺醒吧！<br />\n<br />\n佢為推動社會發展的第一把聲音，大學學生會係時候要團結了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63313da5e58a2a21beeed3da994afce838237391","tid":1185190,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1